40. Sosia prides himself upon being a good and loyal servant. In line 29 he tried to forestall a reminder of his duty. Now the same feeling leads him to inter- pret Simo’s rehearsal of past kindnesses as a reproof. His tone shows vexation. Hence Simo’s reassuring rejoinder.
